<br />Abraço, Marcelo</p></blockquote><div class="replies"><div class="comment depth-2" id="comment-338868"><img alt="A Bóia" class="avatar" height="35" src="//www.gravatar.com/avatar/927cf51b7ac7501d90277ff8aa835ad8?d=mm&amp;s=35" width="35" /><div class="comment-meta"><span class="comment-author"><a href="/" rel="no-follow" target="_blank">A Bóia</a></span><time class="comment-date" datetime="2013-11-06T06:45:57-02:00">06.nov.2013 às 06:45</time><span class="comment-permalink"><a href="/2013/09/costa-amalfitana-roteiro-dicas/comment-page-1#comment-338868">Permalink</a></span><span class="comment-reply_to"><a data-id="338868" href="#comments">Responder</a></span></div><blockquote itemprop="text"><p>Olá, Marcelo! Se você busca agito na costa croata, vá entre final de junho e início de setembro.</p>

